{"type":"message","id":"7cbd0b6f","parentId":"baa586c5","timestamp":"2026-05-09T06:52:43.995Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent a curl command that downloads and executes a script from jimeng.jianying.com. This is a remote script execution - essentially downloading code from the internet and running it with bash. This is a security risk.\n\nLet me think about this:\n\n1. `curl -s https://jimeng.jianying.com/cli | bash` - This fetches a script from jimeng.jianying.com (which appears to be ByteDance's AI image/video generation platform \"即梦\") and executes it directly with bash.\n\n2. This is a legitimate ByteDance service for their AI image generation platform. However, executing arbitrary remote scripts is still a security concern.\n\n3. The user might be asking me to run this command, or they might be sharing something they found and want me to comment on it.\n\nI should NOT just execute this command. I should:\n1. Warn about the security implications of executing remote scripts\n2. Ask for clarification about what this is supposed to do\n3. Offer safer alternatives if appropriate\n\nLet me respond appropriately - this looks like the user wants me to run this command, but I should not blindly execute remote scripts.\n","thinkingSignature":"9ac9fc61b4246c14893ec86a9984612f772509debcc4a6d20a0ac2a78f8fbbe6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n⚠️ **安全警告：执行来源脚木**\n\n这个命令会从 `jimeng.jianying.com` 下载脚本并直接用 `bash` 执行。这存在安全风险：\n\n1. **来源不可控** —— 脚本随时可改，你无法验证它在做什么\n2. **权限过高** —— 直接 pipe 到 bash 绕过了所有安全提示\n3. **传输未加密验证** —— HTTPS 不代表脚本可信\n\n**如果你想安装即梦（字节的AI图片/视频生成平台）的 CLI 工具：**\n- 先看脚本内容：`curl -s https://jimeng.jianying.com/cli | head -50`\n- 确认用途后再决定是否执行\n\n**你是在尝试做什么？** 告诉我目标，我帮你找更安全的方案。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":22407,"output":401,"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22872,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"sto